{"tid":2205928,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"影片證三差人不誠實  官：武力不必要 兩文員脫襲警罪","createTime":"2020-09-17T06:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T08:05:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"10261d593bb6719dbcdc5fca5de7c4ed16d73d3f","tid":2205928,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:58:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/FQHDSRWTCJCKVKU77U544U75QU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FFQHDSRWTCJCKVKU77U544U75QU%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BtArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=df16b77a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FFQHDSRWTCJCKVKU77U544U75QU%2F&h=75e803d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/FQHDSRWTCJCKVKU77U544U75QU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n影片證三差人不誠實 <br />\n官：武力不必要 兩文員脫襲警罪<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年9月1日機場「和你塞」活動，當局封鎖交通，觸發上千市民駕駛私家車「義載」示威者回家。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xnaLUJtP1RvbTfXwu9krv19OBzg=/1661x2215/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YBSQV3VT7VECVEH7NKSPIXXT54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxnaLUJtP1RvbTfXwu9krv19OBzg%3D%2F1661x2215%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYBSQV3VT7VECVEH7NKSPIXXT54.jpg&h=9b457074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■男被告利尚寯獲判無罪後與女友離開法院，稱或就警員作假口供提出私人檢控。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指證人口供與事實不符，要求法官記錄在案，溫官則指這超越其司法管轄權。辯方則指裁判官可轉介個案。溫官謂：「原來我哋咁大權？」<br />\n<br />\n兩被告依次為。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Yfm186anic5Hhqec67zov_KR28M=/590x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WP5NDIXG4BF6NBJIT2SBEYD4GI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYfm186anic5Hhqec67zov_KR28M%3D%2F590x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWP5NDIXG4BF6NBJIT2SBEYD4GI.jpg&h=ce01f51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫紹明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男被告或向警提私人檢控<br />\n<br />\n利的未婚妻獲知無罪後激動至痛哭流涕，兩人年底便「拉埋天窗」，她說「乜嘢判決都好，我都會同佢結婚」，過去利要到警署報到及守宵禁令，已被剝奪自由及承很大壓力困擾。利則多謝律師及拍片人士，若沒有該影片，裁決可能會不同。他直言案件不公平，影片拍到是警員出手推他的未婚妻在先，他或就警員作假供一事提出私人檢控。<br />\n<br />\n溫官昨裁決時特別強調，了解。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n溫官指本案其中三名警方證人的證供，與辯方呈交影片內容明顯不脗合，三人沒說出事實，非誠實可靠，故不接納他們的證供。溫官指警司A追逐可疑人士，其間意外碰到盧，才令盧手持雨傘的手舉起，亦令她向前行出數步。此外，盧當時拿餸菜，屬尋常街坊打扮，惟警員使用不必要的武力，不必要地將她壓向牆邊。<br />\n<br />\n至於利及未婚妻，溫官認為兩人情緒較激動，但沒阻礙警員執法，反而是警員B推撞利女友的胸部，又不斷用胸部頂向兩人，神情兇惡，而利向警員架起前臂，並向警員推去，屬自衞、而非攻擊動作，即使力度大，但所用武力並非不符比例。<br />\n<br />\n兩被告申請訟費，控方稱有指示提出反對，溫官說：「有時指示真係好唔合理。」終批准被告取訟費。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC406/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s3rWs5p2hUP6sSeQFgrokpc-gqA=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LT2S6VGYFZDXDAVSAKT3LMMQOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs3rWs5p2hUP6sSeQFgrokpc-gqA%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLT2S6VGYFZDXDAVSAKT3LMMQOU.jpg&h=7d3071c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女被告盧錦玲事發當日遭警員粗暴壓向牆邊。"},{"pid":"23924264600e86b1cddcdc433e7917760bfecc10","tid":2205928,"uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:59:33.000Z","msg":"大家依家明點解佢要打壓 記者/平民記者 未 ？"},{"pid":"af9dfe0129221a64b36b706a8b5bc04c6b90cec9","tid":2205928,"uid":271516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"朋友聽過佢地講自己有刑事豁免權<br />\n所以做乜都得"},{"pid":"1d9b116316fa97aaaf370cf40807f883c0f290c4","tid":2205928,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"但私刑已行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23604c913f2f63ddaef